text: Jorge Fernández (born 25 September 1968) is a Uruguayan equestrian. He competed in the individual eventing at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Uruguayan male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Uruguay Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Pan American Games medalists in equestrian Category:Pan American Games bronze medalists for Uruguay Category:Equestrians at the 1999 Pan American Games Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
